The package is for the spherical parameterization of SPHARM-RPDM method (Ruan and Murphy, 2018, Bioinformatics)


External packages used:

image_geometric_measures from NS, Yazan Ahed, INRA, David Legland under BSD license

S2 Sampling Toolbox from Anton Semechko under BSD license 

The functions in the 'util' directory are either directly or modified from some functions from SPHARM-MAT package (author: Li Shen, license: GPL v3). We acknowledge the author Shen Li for the package. 
